  "title": "Referral Partner - Web & Software Development",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p></p><p>Shaminder Technologies is a Singapore-based digital solutions company specialising in web development, software development, AI automation,</p><p>content marketing, SEO, and custom dashboards. We build modern, high-quality solutions for SMEs and startups, delivering professional results at</p><p>competitive prices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p></p><p>Join Shaminder Technologies as a Referral Partner and earn 30% commission on every successful project that comes from your referrals. Simply</p><p>connect potential clients with us — we handle all sales conversations, pricing, and project delivery. Work remotely with complete flexibility and</p><p>track your earnings through our private referral portal.</p><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p></p><p>- Identify and refer potential clients (SMEs, startups, entrepreneurs) to Shaminder Technologies by directing them to hello@shaminder.sg</p><p>- Notify the Company of referrals with client name and contact details for tracking and communication purposes</p><p>- Represent Shaminder Technologies in a professional and ethical manner</p><p>- Maintain confidentiality of any proprietary information shared by the Company</p><p></p><p><strong>What We Handle</strong></p><p></p><p>- All client meetings, negotiations, and pricing</p><p>- Project scoping, delivery, and support</p><p></p><p><strong>Compensation & Benefits</strong></p><p></p><p>- 30% commission on total project value (uncapped)</p><p>- Commission paid within 15 days of receiving full client payment</p><p>- Anonymous leaderboard to see your ranking among partners</p><p>- Bonus contests and incentive programmes held regularly (apart from standard commission)</p><p>- Fully remote, flexible hours — work on your own schedule</p><p></p><p><strong>Required Competencies</strong></p><p></p><p>- Ability to communicate clearly and build rapport with business owners</p><p>- Self-motivated with an entrepreneurial mindset to independently identify opportunities</p><p>- Basic understanding of websites and digital solutions (training provided)</p><p>- Access to smartphone and reliable internet connection</p><p>- Based in Singapore or able to engage the Singapore market effectively</p><p></p><p><strong>Preferred Qualifications</strong></p><p></p><p>- Existing network of business contacts, entrepreneurs, or SME owners</p><p>- Experience in sales, business development, or networking roles</p><p></p><p><strong>Agreement Terms</strong></p><p></p><p>- Independent contractor arrangement (not employment)</p><p>- 6-month agreement with renewal option</p><p>- Governed by the laws of Singapore</p>",
